News.headline: Tyrique Hyde On His Development This Season
News.page_title: Tyrique Hyde On His Development This Season
News.URL_keywords: Tyrique Hyde On His Development This Season
News.short_description: Tyrique Hyde on his development with his rise to the first team.
News.description:
"It was nice to make my debut last weekend, I just hope that I get more opportunities like that again."


"I have been working hard in training, trying to make an impression and trying to improve and it is glad for me to see that I am getting recognised and that the hard work is paying off, but I have got to keep going now."


"There is some great players in the team and you can learn of them each day in training. The step up from the youth team to the first team is quite a big step up but I think that I have adapted well."


"In the youth team as well there is good players there and we have a good manager and we are good as a team as well and we have been doing well this season."


"Obviously I know the manager well and if I achieve as half as much as my Dad achieved in his career then I will be happy."


"If we play how we can play and how I know we can play then I think that we will do well and get a result as we are a good side and I believe one of the better sides in the league."
